"You gave Bolson his wood and got him to\n"
"slash his asking price for an old-fashioned\n"
"home from <1.se_co>50,000 rupees<2.re_co> to <3.se_co>3,000 "
"rupees<4.re_co>.\n"
"\n"
"When you have the <5.se_co>3,000 rupees <6.re_co>saved up,\n"
